Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.55,0:00:03.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like fog clearing up in a swoosh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.42,0:00:05.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see through both romance and cases!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.48,0:00:07.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A bistro with a Showa Era atmosphere...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.15,0:00:08.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A cunning trick a place without elbow room!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.03,0:00:10.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:12.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.61,0:00:14.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.14,0:02:08.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.22,0:02:09.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have special discounts!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.03,0:02:11.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.39,0:02:17.02,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Nakamura Susumu (64)\NCompany Employee and Horse-Racing Fan
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.15,0:02:14.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.65,0:02:17.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The main race was an outrageous upset!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.15,0:02:20.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aww, out-of-the-money!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.40,0:02:23.70,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Ougi Chihiro(35)\NJapanese Dance Instructor
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.03,0:02:23.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't possibly win thanks to that giant-killin' underdog!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.08,0:02:28.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Any chance you guys bet on the Touto Derby?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.20,0:02:32.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Loyal customers who love horse\Nbetting often come here on Saturdays.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:36.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We always come here soon after a race ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.79,0:02:39.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And talk about who wins or loses.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:40.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:42.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:45.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To tell the truth, I'm also a bettor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.02,0:02:46.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.93,0:02:48.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please let me take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:49.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.56,0:02:56.06,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Shinohara Masao (25)\NFreeter
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.48,0:02:53.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Trifecta on numbers 1,2, and 3?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.02,0:02:56.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't these today's winning tickets at 100-1 odds!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.67,0:02:57.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.09,0:03:02.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's exactly it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:05.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, you're really lucky, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.74,0:03:10.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the cat's out of the bag, the lucky yours\Ntruly shall treat everyone here tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.90,0:03:12.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, these tickets...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.83,0:03:13.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hostess!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.79,0:03:16.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please bring each of us some drinks for starters!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.04,0:03:18.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.04,0:03:20.25,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Mishima Satsuki (50)\NHostess
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.09,0:03:20.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sir, aren't you a generous one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.80,0:03:23.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nah, you're flattering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:29.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm, what was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.70,0:03:33.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you mean this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.92,0:03:35.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just a little help.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.66,0:03:38.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since my shop's so narrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:40.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I find it easier to move about on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.64,0:03:43.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.74,0:03:46.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.92,0:03:54.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder whether or not Lady Luck will knock on my door as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:57.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you getting your retirement allowance soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.08,0:03:59.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Retirement allowance?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.75,0:04:01.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.17,0:04:02.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not all that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:05.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, say...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.38,0:04:09.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why not splurge that money and take me to Awaii-hay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.58,0:04:10.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.89,0:04:14.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh my, quite a luxurious player, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:16.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Moneybags.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.66,0:04:19.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, instead of some cheap sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.61,0:04:22.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't I get you something more high-class?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.68,0:04:24.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:28.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you go to Shounan Hawaiian\NCenter or something like that instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:30.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:32.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Each year I'd visit the hotel over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.83,0:04:35.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And hold a presentation on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.20,0:04:36.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that may be a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.04,0:04:38.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yo, let the show begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:40.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What presentation?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.61,0:04:45.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm a Japanese traditional dance instructor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.07,0:04:57.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:05:00.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whenever you're drunk, you always go overboard like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.54,0:05:02.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since you're going as far as to hold presentations...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.94,0:05:06.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Certainly your academy business must be blooming, I assume?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.11,0:05:11.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That can't be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.66,0:05:16.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once during her presentation, she accidentally\Nslipped and did a split while falling down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.93,0:05:20.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An academy with such a lousy instructor can never bloom!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.25,0:05:24.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dont'cha go ahead and recite that sort of nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.65,0:05:26.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Presentations, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.40,0:05:28.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a wonder some people never know their place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.86,0:05:30.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say what!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:31.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I dare you say that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:33.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You sure that's wise?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:35.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Talking back to me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:39.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.02,0:05:46.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:47.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.65,0:05:51.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After I left my hometown and came here,\Nthis is the bistro I happened to run into.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.75,0:05:56.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now it feels completely like Mom's cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.10,0:06:02.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This guy wanted to be a top restaurant chef so\Nbad, he left home for Tokyo if memory serves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.08,0:06:05.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a saying that goes, "Dreams may'shatter, but whatever."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.62,0:06:09.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you still working at the fish market I introduced you to?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.87,0:06:12.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes... thanks to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:15.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hostess, you're good at taking care of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.43,0:06:19.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you want to be a chef, you need to train\Nyour/eyes to discern quality fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.95,0:06:20.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.02,0:06:22.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinohara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.12,0:06:26.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been great training for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.23,0:06:30.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, so that's why you took on the fish market job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:34.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That reminds me, why are your pants all wet like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.53,0:06:38.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This happened when I was walking on the street earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.44,0:06:42.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the hostess "happened" to splash water on you with a bucket.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.37,0:06:44.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How'd you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.95,0:06:46.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you did that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.87,0:06:49.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't tell right from wrong at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.17,0:06:53.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a trick you always use to reel in the lucky horse\Nbettors who'd won a little cash to spend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.06,0:06:57.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you keep this up, divine punishment will ensue.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.62,0:06:59.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop badmouthing the hostess already!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.62,0:07:02.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't get any job offers after I came to Tokyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.41,0:07:05.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But she helped me out when I was about to lose hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.11,0:07:07.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's my savior!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.35,0:07:10.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, don't get all worked up like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.83,0:07:13.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been feeling a strong chill for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.96,0:07:15.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.46,0:07:17.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The walls are plywood patched with iron plates...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.91,0:07:20.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So wind will come in through this gap.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.03,0:07:24.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This chill's getting me too, so I'm going to the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:26.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, stand up and make way already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.83,0:07:28.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lady's coming through.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.62,0:07:31.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No room to swing a cat hereâ€”can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:39.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that we've gotten our asses up, I\Nmight as well go buy some cigarettes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.77,0:07:43.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I need to withdraw some money before the ATM closes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.26,0:07:46.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll take a puff too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.35,0:07:57.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tobacco,tobacco...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.99,0:07:58.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.06,0:08:01.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did I put it in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.11,0:08:17.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think Dad recently frequents this area to get his drink fix.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.80,0:08:23.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To think he's able to drink sake in such a smoky place!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:25.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.57,0:08:28.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:31.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're taking a puff at a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.78,0:08:32.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.83,0:08:34.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you guys doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.41,0:08:37.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So everyone's returned, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.59,0:08:45.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.77,0:08:47.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hostess!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.86,0:08:51.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hostess, please hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.53,0:08:52.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hostess!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:54.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.01,0:09:04.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that was a summary of this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.01,0:09:08.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The single stab in the chest from this knife was her cause of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:10.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the handle of the murder weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.59,0:09:12.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's the bistro's trademark "Satsuki".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.44,0:09:15.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All the knives in the hostess's shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.98,0:09:18.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Apparently have that particular symbol on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.19,0:09:22.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We did not find any signs of rummaging in the bistro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.86,0:09:25.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can assume this was unlikely a crime for gain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.66,0:09:27.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:29.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you here, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.62,0:09:30.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.95,0:09:35.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since I won the long shot, I bought dinner\Nfor all the regular customers here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.58,0:09:38.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like someone's having lots of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:41.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, it's nothing like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.26,0:09:46.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, at the time of incident, everyone including\Nme had stepped outside the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.89,0:09:47.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.30,0:09:50.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the hostess was all by herself in the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.31,0:09:55.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And due to those frosted glass stripes, nobody\Ncan see what's going on from the outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.03,0:09:56.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.86,0:10:01.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means the only ones who knew the\Nhostess was alone were these customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.57,0:10:05.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So within five minutes after everyone's departure...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.32,0:10:08.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone amongst the customers killed the hostess?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.37,0:10:12.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, let's hear what the customers have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.33,0:10:16.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, you want to question us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.17,0:10:23.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Judging from the circumstances of the scene, it's highly probable\Nthat someone among you three committed the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.30,0:10:25.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop spewing nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.63,0:10:29.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As such, during the five minutes around the incident...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.26,0:10:31.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What were your whereabouts and actions?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.43,0:10:33.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please tell us in detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.69,0:10:37.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That reminds me, at that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:43.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even after everyone else left the shop, only\NOugi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} failed to do for quite a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.48,0:10:44.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps Ougi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.15,0:10:48.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Purposely waited for a chance to be alone with the hostess?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.23,0:10:51.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why'd I have to do something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.91,0:10:57.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me, you've been borrowing from the hostess\Nsince your academy was on the verge of closing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.04,0:10:58.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.08,0:11:02.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That hostess always puts on a smile when lending..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:06.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But rumor has it she would turn into a demon upon collections.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.22,0:11:08.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.47,0:11:11.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So did you really borrow money from the hostess?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.89,0:11:13.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.97,0:11:18.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Recently she's been demanding me\Nto pay my debt, almost every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.48,0:11:23.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I was about to leave the shop earlier,\Nshe again pressed me to pay up today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.78,0:11:27.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you flew into a rage and picked up the knife at the counter...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.94,0:11:28.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.78,0:11:31.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The argument became pointless, so I stormed off like a shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:35.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But then the hostess ended up dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.50,0:11:37.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I merely found it hard to mention all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.66,0:11:38.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah-le?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.00,0:11:42.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This person's sleeve looks kind of wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.34,0:11:45.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.55,0:11:48.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I recall, you're a southpaw, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.76,0:11:50.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you were drinking wine...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:51.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Using the fan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.14,0:11:54.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And pinning the tack, you used your left hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.31,0:11:57.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason why your left sleeve is wet...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.89,0:12:03.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was because you washed off the blood in the restroom\Nwhich you got from stabbing the hostess, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.31,0:12:06.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The water faucet in the restroom was broken\Nand the water sprayed up, that's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.28,0:12:11.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As a precaution, let the medical examiner\Ntest her for a luminol reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.11,0:12:11.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.99,0:12:14.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, this way please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.08,0:12:18.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, Nakamura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.29,0:12:20.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.58,0:12:24.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After you said you were buying cigarettes and left the shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:27.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You turned right on the street ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.13,0:12:32.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, I was certain that you came from\Nthe opposite direction upon return.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.47,0:12:36.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though the cigarette vending machine's down here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.06,0:12:39.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you return via the opposite direction?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.56,0:12:40.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.77,0:12:42.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because the vending machine's out of cigarettes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.98,0:12:44.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went all the way to the convenience store on Big Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.92,0:12:45.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.23,0:12:48.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've discovered the hostess's notebook...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.94,0:12:53.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it shows that Nakamura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} has been\Nmaking monthly payments of 100,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.82,0:12:56.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is too much of a payment for a drinking tab.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.87,0:12:58.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of money is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.83,0:13:00.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.72,0:13:05.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, the hostess got hold of my secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.69,0:13:06.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:12.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been embezzling money from my company\Nto lash out on horse-betting...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.54,0:13:17.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And she blackmailed me saying she'd break\Nthe news to my company if I didn't pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.18,0:13:19.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I didn't kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.68,0:13:22.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really walked to the convenience store on Big Street!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.19,0:13:26.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, Shinohara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.92,0:13:27.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.40,0:13:32.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In this notebook, we've found records\Nof your name, Shinohara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.49,0:13:35.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And fish names like "horse mackerel" or "squid".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.49,0:13:35.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.35,0:13:38.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since I'm working part-time at a fish market...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.24,0:13:41.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sometimes I receive orders from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.87,0:13:43.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess that's the record of those?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.83,0:13:47.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What were you doing within the five minutes after you left the shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.92,0:13:51.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since I didn't have cash on me, I went\Nto withdraw some at a nearby ATM.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.97,0:13:54.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here's my receipt.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.47,0:13:56.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.97,0:13:59.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The time confirms it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.47,0:14:04.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After Shinohara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} stepped out of the\Nbistro, he walked towards Front Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.45,0:14:10.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the ATM's right here, it's impossible\Nfor him to secretly return to the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.65,0:14:14.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Given that there are no inconsistencies on his ATM receipt...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.81,0:14:16.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems impossible for him to have killed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.20,0:14:25.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I recall, Uncle said he bought dinner for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.79,0:14:29.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's in the knife stand are all Japanese kitchen knives.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.15,0:14:32.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.26,0:14:37.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Juice?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.76,0:14:39.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He mentioned the hostess was a non-drinker.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.31,0:14:43.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A brandy glass?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.85,0:14:48.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This hasn't been used.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.81,0:14:56.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The brandy bottle has been...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.61,0:15:21.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.39,0:15:23.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.89,0:15:25.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The trick to this case!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:31.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, dozing off during an investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.48,0:15:34.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, might as well attach my mini speaker now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:36.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.08,0:15:39.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't just wander around like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.79,0:15:40.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.61,0:15:41.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.58,0:15:47.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to the test results, no luminol reaction\Ncould be detected from Ougi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.57,0:15:51.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moreover, we also confirmed with\Nthe convenient store on Big Street...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.21,0:15:54.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That Nakamura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was indeed there to make a purchase.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.87,0:15:58.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guess I don't need this today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.65,0:16:01.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.08,0:16:03.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please come to the station for further questioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.96,0:16:06.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, there's no need for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.18,0:16:09.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I shall solve the case right here on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.06,0:16:13.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, have you figured out who the culprit is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.92,0:16:14.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.34,0:16:18.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The brandy glass left on the cutting board...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.53,0:16:21.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Clued me in to the culprit's identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.74,0:16:23.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Brandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.66,0:16:27.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please pour me a glassful, Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.95,0:16:29.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it, he freaking woke up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.10,0:16:35.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.92,0:16:37.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.59,0:16:40.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Never mind me, go check out the bistro counter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.17,0:16:44.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ougi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.60,0:16:46.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nakamura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.had Japanese sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.29,0:16:47.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.76,0:16:50.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinohara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.had some sour mix.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.64,0:16:54.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's more, on the cutting board you can see a\Nglass of juice the hostess had been drinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.06,0:16:58.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And a brandy glass that hadn't been used at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:17:00.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.65,0:17:02.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About that brandy glass...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.53,0:17:04.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder who that was for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.51,0:17:09.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,None of us customers ordered brandy\Nbefore we stepped out of the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.87,0:17:11.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's indeed out of place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.58,0:17:13.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at the highest place of the shelf.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.60,0:17:19.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can see the brandy bottle on the shelf has been moved a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.98,0:17:25.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's likely the culprit, after going out the shop,\Nmade a phone call from the outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.97,0:17:30.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And placed an order for the fancy brandy on the shelf.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.76,0:17:34.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps telling lies about that expensive\Nbeverage being a treat from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.94,0:17:37.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order for the short hostess to reach the brandy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.44,0:17:42.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She had to stand on her tiptoes by\Nleaning against the shelf and wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.19,0:17:46.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit used the chance and pushed\Nthe knife through the gap in the wall...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.72,0:17:51.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you saying they stabbed her from outside the shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.23,0:17:56.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the back of the shop, there's a dark alley\Nthat allows passage of one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.44,0:17:59.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the wall made of plywood patched with iron plates...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.75,0:18:01.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Has a thin gap on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.42,0:18:04.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit made a phone call in the back alley...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.84,0:18:07.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lured the hostess near the wall...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.59,0:18:10.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And inserted the knife in the gap and killed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.89,0:18:15.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The knife was presumably stolen from the shop beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.56,0:18:19.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, when we discovered the hostess...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.07,0:18:22.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was lying flat on the counter facing us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.40,0:18:23.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.65,0:18:26.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If she was stabbed near the wall, she\Nwouldn't have collapsed like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.99,0:18:31.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hostess's chair is the type that can\Nturn around in a narrow counter...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.96,0:18:33.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A swivel chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.28,0:18:37.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ironically, the force from the hostess's collapse\Nexerted on the chair caused it to turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.58,0:18:41.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And she fell on the counter facing the front as a result.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.30,0:18:45.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But since the knife has a handle...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.22,0:18:48.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't it be unable to go through the wall gap?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.05,0:18:51.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, how goes it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.64,0:18:52.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.87,0:18:54.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The handle is blocked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.85,0:18:57.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What if the handle wasn't on the knife?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.06,0:18:59.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.48,0:19:04.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The chef's knives we use in preparing Western\Ncuisine have rivets attached on the handle...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.19,0:19:07.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Japanese knives simply have blades inserted in their handles.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.47,0:19:09.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Very easy to pull apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.53,0:19:12.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, it's just Hike what Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} said!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.54,0:19:14.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.09,0:19:17.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit allowed us to discover the body...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.79,0:19:21.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While walking behind the counter, pretending to be worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.79,0:19:24.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then slipped the handle back on the blade...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.38,0:19:27.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the same time holding the hostess up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.34,0:19:29.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.76,0:19:30.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.43,0:19:32.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.82,0:19:35.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The person who had the need to deploy\Nthe trick using the plug-fit knife...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.35,0:19:37.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Had to rush to her first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.14,0:19:39.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinohara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.61,0:19:41.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was none other than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.45,0:19:45.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I was at the ATM...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.59,0:19:46.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.53,0:19:47.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He has an alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.94,0:19:48.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.40,0:19:51.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the crime was committed at the back of the shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.91,0:19:53.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ATM would've been surprisingly close.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.28,0:19:55.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His alibi means nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.21,0:19:59.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we're talking about Shinohara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} who's\Naiming to become a top restaurant chef...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:03.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's possible that he knows well about the fact\Nthat Japanese knife handles are removable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.96,0:20:07.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have solid evidence confirming that I did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.17,0:20:10.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The envelope of the receipt you showed us earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.12,0:20:11.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw smudges on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.55,0:20:16.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's iron rust, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.64,0:20:24.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During the crime, it's likely you were holding the knife blade\Nwithout its handle in your hand with a handkerchief.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.40,0:20:27.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As such, the rust on the wall's iron plate got on your handkerchief.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.14,0:20:33.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Without noticing that, you put the handkerchief back\Ninto the same pocket where the envelope was.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.41,0:20:35.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the rust got on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.29,0:20:38.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we compare the iron plate and the envelope rust...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.87,0:20:41.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guarantee that we will confirm a .
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.56,0:20:44.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.46,0:20:47.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wasn't the hostess your savior?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.67,0:20:48.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hell no!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.54,0:20:52.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason why that woman introduced\Nme to the job with a kind facade...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.99,0:20:56.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was because she could use me to steal produce from the market!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.38,0:20:57.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.01,0:21:01.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At first she merely asked for leftovers or damaged fish meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.02,0:21:04.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But then her greed escalated...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.96,0:21:09.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Recently she even pesteringly demanded me to bring her\Nfree high-end produce like sea urchins and salmon roe!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.26,0:21:11.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't take it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.36,0:21:14.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I told her I was going to quit my job...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.68,0:21:18.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,if you quit, I will expose everything you did so far at the market.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.24,0:21:22.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When that happens, you'll go to jail for theft.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.75,0:21:25.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that was per your instructions, Hostess...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.08,0:21:26.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.55,0:21:30.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where on earth can you find solid proof\Nhat I instructed you to do so?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.59,0:21:33.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the only one who'll get caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.86,0:21:37.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, since you can't possibly become a top chef after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.30,0:21:38.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's probably better for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.72,0:21:42.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I could never bring myself to abandon\Nmy dream of becoming a top chef!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.06,0:21:43.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.39,0:21:48.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, you used a knife, equivalent to the lifeline of a top chef...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.27,0:21:50.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As a weapon for murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.40,0:21:52.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As such, you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.40,0:21:56.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No longer qualified to become a top chef, am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.72,0:23:29.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.84,0:23:33.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That reminds me, Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.60,0:23:35.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say you won the long shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.34,0:23:37.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.47,0:23:39.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't those all 100 yen tickets?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.33,0:23:45.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though I won the long shot, the payoff wasn't\Nmuch since I only wagered 100 yen each...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.69,0:23:49.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But since vanity got the best of me,\NI shot the works and am all broke!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.98,0:23:51.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.62,0:23:52.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.81,0:23:53.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pretty please!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.72,0:23:54.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.27,0:23:58.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will he be able to gallop away from this?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.66,0:24:04.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{text from 635} Let your body soak in its energy to the fullest.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.07,0:24:06.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to go on a yoga diet too?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.55,0:24:09.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The lawsuit was against me...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.82,0:24:14.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Atsuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} lost her lawsuit...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.94,0:24:17.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And must've been deep in shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.58,0:24:19.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{wrong text}What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.15,0:24:21.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since lack of sleep is bad for your body's beauty...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.91,0:24:24.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to solve it right here and right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.40,0:24:29.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,BEWARE OF DIETING
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.59,0:24:47.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.76,0:24:50.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Microwave
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.41,0:24:51.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.53,0:24:52.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whay the haste? Still too early for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.89,0:24:54.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Viewers, let's meet again around then.
